<figureCitation box="[277,309,1059,1083]" captionStart="Figure 20-23" captionStartId="36.[192,276,1730,1752]" captionTargetBox="[241,1422,209,1701]" captionTargetId="figure-21@36.[213,1419,192,1731]" captionTargetPageId="36" captionText="Figure 20-23. Aedeagus images. 20) Sonoma baylessae, aedeagus (dorsal view). 21) Sonoma brasstownensis, aedeagus (dorsal view). 22) Sonoma nicholsae, aedeagus (dorsal view). 23) Sonoma gilae, aedeagus (dorsal view). Scale lines equal 0.1 mm. Right side of figure is anatomical left." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5164850" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5164850/files/figure.png" pageId="12" pageNumber="11">21</figureCitation>
